graph TD
    G[Guardian] -->|declares| PCP[PrincipalCapabilityProfile<br/>on-device, 8 dimensions]
    PCP -->|read by| Agent[Agent]
    Agent -->|computes| IM[InteractionModality<br/>adapted communication plan]
    IM -->|before consent| CCC{ConsentCapacityCheck<br/>capacity_signal >= threshold?}
    CCC -->|proceed/simplify| CR[ConsentRecord<br/>with PACE metadata]
    CCC -->|defer| WAIT[Wait for next valid window]
    CCC -->|escalate| GN[Notify Guardian]
    CR -->|governed by| AIC[AdaptiveInteractionContract<br/>time windows, option limits,<br/>violation policy]
    AIC -->|outcome feeds| WT[WelfareTrace<br/>accessibility metrics]
    WT -->|declining trajectory| G

    style PCP fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style CCC fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107
    style AIC fill:#cce5ff,stroke:#0d6efd
    style GN fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#dc3545
